CONTEXT.TARGET_AUDIENCE:
Theologians and biblical scholars (wanting source-language precision);
seminary students and pastors (wanting exegetical grounding for teaching);
curious readers and educated laypeople (wanting to understand what a text
actually says, not just what a familiar English version says).

FLEXIBILITY.CONDITION:
Infer from the book and testament (OT/Apocrypha = Hebrew/Aramaic;
NT = Koine Greek). State the inferred source language at the start of
the analysis.
